---
// src/cards/Card2.astro
import SectionShell from "../components/SectionShell.astro";
---

<SectionShell variant="light">
  <!-- Header (simple variation, no rule) -->
  <h2 class="font-brand mb-6 text-sm font-bold tracking-wider uppercase">
    Who is epic swagger?
  </h2>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div
    class="font-inter max-w-prose py-5 text-3xl font-extralight text-balance"
  >
    <p class="mb-4 text-sm md:text-base">
      An alliance of elite coaches specializing in fitness, nutrition, and
      mindset who are experts in aesthetic optimization and performance
      transformation. Our mission? To instill the principles of discipline and
      excellence that builds unshakable confidence and magnetic attractiveness
      in every area of your life.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4 text-sm md:text-base">
      We help you develop an unshakable presence rooted in self-belief, purpose,
      and authenticity. It's the quiet confidence that comes from doing the
      work, knowing who you are, and walking into every room with alignment,
      intention, and impact. It's not arrogance, it's assurance. It's not
      vanity, it's vitality. It's not loud, it's locked in. Swagger is when your
      energy speaks before you do, and your actions echo long after you leave
      the room.
    </p>
  </div>
</SectionShell>
